metadata.name: Androgyny
metadata.description:
blacked out of my mind
too many feelings and body trembling, atmosphere that seems to condense and lacking air,
unable to breathe,
my form feeling like it's been torn away,
and with that feeling comes the pain,
I was on fire,
drowning in my own despair,
unable to scream for help,
gradually losing sight of life,
collapsing into the earth,
like being reborn.
